        "html_6A9nxf": {
          "type": "html",
          "settings": {
            "code": "<div style=\"width:100%; padding:40px 20px; box-sizing:border-box;\">\n  \n  <div style=\"max-width:1000px; margin:0 auto;\">\n\n    <!-- Main Heading -->\n    <h1 style=\"color:#12395E; font-size:32px; margin-bottom:15px; text-align:center; line-height:1.3;\">\n      Understanding TipTop360: Vision, Mission & Values\n    </h1>\n\n    <p style=\"color:#202020; font-size:18px; text-align:center; margin-bottom:40px; line-height:1.6;\">\n      The purpose, promise, and principles that guide everything we do.\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Vision -->\n    <div style=\"background:#ffffff; padding:30px; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); margin-bottom:30px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"color:#12395E; font-size:24px; margin-top:0;\">\n        🌟 Our Vision\n      </h2>\n      <p style=\"color:#202020; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7;\">\n        To be the most trusted destination for feel-good, everyday products — curated with care, delivered with speed, \n        and loved for making life easier. We believe shopping should bring a sense of joy, simplicity, and confidence. \n        At <strong style=\"color:#12395E;\">TipTop360</strong>, we aim to turn every shopping experience into a moment of delight.\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"color:#202020; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7;\">\n        We envision a future where innovation leads the way — becoming a pioneer in our industry through cutting-edge \n        solutions, exceptional service, and sustainable growth that empowers both customers and communities.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Mission -->\n    <div style=\"background:#ffffff; padding:30px; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); margin-bottom:30px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"color:#12395E; font-size:24px; margin-top:0;\">\n        🎯 Our Mission\n      </h2>\n      <p style=\"color:#202020; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7;\">\n        We save you time and effort by handpicking smart, problem-solving finds — delivered fast and backed by personal, \n        human support. Our mission is to make your life easier, whether you're solving everyday challenges or discovering \n        products that make you smile.\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"color:#202020; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7;\">\n        We strive to exceed expectations by building lasting relationships based on trust, collaboration, and integrity. \n        Your success and satisfaction guide every decision we make.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Values -->\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:35px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"color:#12395E; font-size:24px; margin-bottom:20px;\">\n        💛 Our Values\n      </h2>\n\n      <!-- Value 1 -->\n      <div style=\"background:#ffffff; padding:25px; border-left:5px solid #12395E; margin-bottom:20px; border-radius:8px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color:#202020; margin-top:0; font-size:18px;\">🌟 Curated with Purpose</h3>\n        <p style=\"color:#202020; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0;\">\n          We only offer what we’d use ourselves — no fluff, just smart and useful products. \n          Every item is selected with care to simplify your life and add meaningful value.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Value 2 -->\n      <div style=\"background:#ffffff; padding:25px; border-left:5px solid #202020; margin-bottom:20px; border-radius:8px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color:#202020; margin-top:0; font-size:18px;\">🙋‍♀️ Customer First, Always</h3>\n        <p style=\"color:#202020; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0;\">\n          Every decision starts with your experience. From fast shipping to helpful support, \n          we treat you like family and make your satisfaction our top priority.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Value 3 -->\n      <div style=\"background:#ffffff; padding:25px; border-left:5px solid #12395E; margin-bottom:20px; border-radius:8px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color:#202020; margin-top:0; font-size:18px;\">⚡ Fast, Friendly & Reliable</h3>\n        <p style=\"color:#202020; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0;\">\n          We move quickly, deliver reliably, and treat you like a person — not just an order number. \n          Our team ensures a smooth, efficient, and enjoyable experience from start to finish.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Value 4 -->\n      <div style=\"background:#ffffff; padding:25px; border-left:5px solid #202020; border-radius:8px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color:#202020; margin-top:0; font-size:18px;\">😊 Feel-Good Finds</h3>\n        <p style=\"color:#202020; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0;\">\n          We believe shopping should spark joy. Every product should solve a problem, lighten a load, \n          or make someone smile — elevating your everyday life.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Core Principles -->\n      <div style=\"margin-top:30px; padding-top:20px; border-top:1px solid #ddd;\">\n        <p style=\"color:#202020; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7;\">\n          <strong>Integrity, Innovation, and Customer Focus</strong> form the foundation of our culture. \n          We operate transparently and ethically, encourage creativity, actively listen to feedback, \n          and continuously improve to build stronger relationships and mutual success.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Closing -->\n    <div style=\"text-align:center; margin-top:40px;\">\n      <p style=\"font-size:18px; color:#12395E; font-weight:bold; margin-bottom:10px;\">\n        Built on purpose. Driven by care. Focused on you.\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"font-size:20px; color:#202020; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0;\">\n        That’s the TipTop360 promise.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>",
            "width": "100%",
            "align": "auto"
          }
        }
      },
